Accelerated aging in bipolar disorders: An exploratory study of six epigenetic 
clocks.

Bourdon C(1), Etain B(2), Spano L(3), Belzeaux R(4), Leboyer M(5), 
Delahaye-Duriez A(6), Ibrahim EC(7), Lutz PE(8), Gard S(9), Schwan R(10), 
